TheSource v0.2.0 (Release date: 2020-02-)
==============

Changes:

* Make gridIDW a CPP optimized function
* Added gridODV for gridding like ODV
* Added gridKrig for krige-based gridding
* Updated build.section to carrry LAT/LON information
* Updated add.section.bathy to use LAT/LON info

TheSource v0.2.0 (Release date: 2019-11-)
==============

Changes:

* Major improvements to gridding function performance
* Reorganized gridding functions
* Renamed add.contour to add.section.contour
* Rewrote add.section.contour


TheSource v0.1.8 (Release date: 2019-11-3)
==============

Changes:

* Updated is.within() to accept multiple bounds
* Include cruise name in load.beta() and summarize.beta()
* Added load.beta.icpms() for yield analysis
* Fixed DESCRIPTION file that prevented install


TheSource v0.1.7 (Release date: 2019-10-05)
==============

Changes:

* Improved documentation for add.colorbar()
* Enabled horizontal support for add.colorbar()

* Improved load.beta() function
* Added summarize.beta()
* Added correct.beta.names()

* Improved build.section() performance (x5)
* Removed neighborhood from build.section()
* Added print.nc()
* Added load.roms()
* Added get.roms.time()
* Added get.zlevel.roms()
* Added load.ltrans()
* Updated uncertainty in gridders to 1e-12
* Removed "old" gridders
* Include gridding function in grid.meta for all sections
* Improved out of range color handling in plot.section()

* Added conv.uM.to.ml()
* Reworked which.within() and added is.within()


TheSource v0.1.6 (Release date: 2019-10-01)
==============

Changes:

* Updated calc.k.reuer() to reduce risk of breaking and to improve computation
* Added is.inside() function


TheSource v0.1.5 (Release date: 2019-09-19)
==============

Changes:

* Initial NEWS release
* First publically available release, all source files should be updated to reflect TheSource package
* Renamed colnames in the results of parameter.search to reflect cost function arguments
